[[!meta title="Tails 1.0 is out"]]
[[!tag announce]]

Tails, The Amnesic Incognito Live System, version 1.0, is out.

All users must upgrade as soon as possible: this release fixes
[[numerous security issues|security/Numerous_security_holes_in_0.23]].

[[!toc levels=1]]

# Changes

Notable user-visible changes include:

* Security fixes

* Major new features

* Bugfixes

* Minor improvements

See the [online
Changelog](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/tails/plain/debian/changelog)
for technical details.

